{"id":399,"date":"2008-05-22T11:31:36","date_gmt":"2008-05-22T03:31:36","guid":{"rendered":"http://xbeta.info/?p=399"},"modified":"2008-05-22T11:31:36","modified_gmt":"2008-05-22T03:31:36","slug":"ask-quick-launch","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/ask-quick-launch.htm","title":{"rendered":"讨论: 快速启动程序的工具软件，FARR最好？"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>（<strong>本文要点：超强软件FARR </strong><a href=\"http://www.donationcoder.com/Software/Mouser/findrun/index.html\">Find and Run Robot</a><strong>！</strong>）如上一篇所说，有些软件是多人关注，而我不用的，比如快速启动程序的工具。为什么？因为我选择了<a href=\"http://xbeta.info/win-run.htm\" target=\"_blank\">最绿色最高效，用win+r启动常用程序和文档</a>的做法，还有<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/46dac66f010005cf\" target=\"_blank\">AutoHotkey:帮助win run更方便</a>。</p>\n<p>大家可以各自列举一下自己所用工具的优缺点。对于常见而著名的几款软件我就不列举了。</p>\n<p>我只补充一款，很特别的一款，国内知之甚少，而我认为功能最强大的一款——虽然我没用过，但可以相信我的眼力——就是拥有众多扩展的FARR！来自Screenshot Captor的作者，也是DonationCoder网站创建者Mouser。他是一位有能力（无论是编程还是组织）、有想法的人。</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://www.donationcoder.com/Software/Mouser/findrun/screenshots/album/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http://www.donationcoder.com/Software/Mouser/findrun/screenshots/farr2a1s.png\" alt=\"farr screenshot\" width=\"286\" height=\"153\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.donationcoder.com/Software/Mouser/findrun/screenshots/album/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http://www.donationcoder.com/Software/Mouser/findrun/screenshots/farr2a2s.png\" alt=\"farr screenshot\" width=\"280\" height=\"160\" /></a></p>\n<p>LifeHacker正在进行<a href=\"http://lifehacker.com/392136/best-application-launchers\" target=\"_blank\">快速启动软件的投票评选</a>，大家可以去看看。我记得以前他们评过一次，FARR是很领先的，超越了Launchy，我认为结论客观。以前我也曾在留言中提过FARR，但未引起大家的重视。</p>\n<p>详见：<a href=\"http://www.donationcoder.com/Software/Mouser/findrun/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">FARR (Find and Run Robot)主页</a>，可以多关注其扩展。</p>\n<p>有兴趣的网友：<br />\n可以把主页的文本译为中文，贴到留言中，我整理成中文主页。（参见已完成的<a href=\"http://xbeta.info/screenshot_captor.htm\">Screenshot Captor主页</a>）<br />\n也可以制作FARR的汉化版本。<br />\n我正联系作者Mouser，征求许可。></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>（本文要点：超强软件FARR Find and Run Robot！）如上一篇所说，有些软件是多人关注，而我不 [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["未分类","系统工具"],"tags":["quick-launch","all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/399"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=399"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/399/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=399"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=399"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=399"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}